[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0330","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0330.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0161","title":"Cisco IOS 访问控制列表绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 10.3 在配置 tacacs-ds 或 tacacs 关键字时，扩展 IP 访问控制列表（ACL）存在过滤绕过漏洞。当使用 TACACS+ 认证的扩展 ACL 规则应用于接口时，系统未能正确匹配数据包与规则条目，导致实际生效的过滤策略与配置不符。远程攻击者可利用此缺陷绕过 ACL 限制，未经授权访问受保护的网络资源。该漏洞影响运行 Cisco IOS 10.3 的设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0161"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-07-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:43.920","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 11.0 及以上版本，避免使用已废弃的 tacacs-ds/tacacs 关键词，改用 tacacs+ 协议。配置访问控制列表时确保标准 ACL 与扩展 ACL 规则顺序正确，避免过滤绕过。在无法升级的环境中，移除使用缺陷关键词的 ACL 条目，改用基于命名或标准 ACL 的替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/797"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0330.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0165","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0165.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0066","title":"John S. Roberts AnyForm CGI 参数分号注入远程命令执行漏洞","description":"John S.2 Roberts AnyForm 1.0/2.0 是一款 CGI 表单处理程序，其存在远程命令执行漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在 CGI 参数中插入分号（;）注入恶意系统命令，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 AnyForm 1.0 和 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 9.8，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0066"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1995-07-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.853","remediation":"立即停止使用 AnyForm CGI 脚本，删除或禁用服务器上所有 anyform.cgi/AnyForm 相关 CGI 程序。此软件已停止维护且不再更新，建议替换为支持输入过滤的现代表单处理方案，或迁移至 WSGI/FastCGI 架构以隔离 CGI 执行环境。如无法替换，在网络层面限制 CGI 目录的执行权限并禁用分号作为参数分隔符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/719","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19557","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0066","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f06304a9243ce013bfbf7cea427539f6409c0a05/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0066.md","https://github.com/krafthack-by-techday/Night-s-watch/blob/30ae1bcc335306fe4c5507b2c629cae4932e515e/cve/nvd/CVE-1999-0066_0f0c3530-7572-4860-a943-991d78115c24","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/AnyForm.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0066.json","https://github.com/vicentewncosta/CVE/blob/f53f621dd0bde68d4b3c8ad5314ae2c5a0197af8/DOCUMENTATION.md","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0165.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0165.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0165.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0313","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0313.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0151","title":"SATAN 会话密钥泄露漏洞","description":"SATAN（Security Analysis Tool for Auditing Networks）安全审计工具的 Web 界面存在会话密钥泄露漏洞。当用户在使用 SATAN 分析工具的同时通过 Web 浏览器访问其他恶意站点时，攻击者可通过跨站请求等方式窃取 SATAN 的会话密钥，进而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响早期版本的 SATAN 工具，攻击条件为用户在运行 SATAN 时浏览了攻击者控制的网站，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0151"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-04-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.540","remediation":"CVE-1999-0151 年代久远，SATAN 工具已停止维护，**根本修复方案是停止使用 SATAN**，迁移至 Nessus、OpenVAS 等现代漏洞扫描器。若临时使用 SATAN Web 界面，应采取以下缓解措施：(1) 使用独立浏览器/配置文件运行 SATAN 界面，切勿在 SATAN 会话期间访问其他网站，防止 Referer 泄露 session key；(2) 配置浏览器或代理插件（如 Referer Control）在访问 SATAN 界面时禁止发送 Referer 头；(3) 在防火墙/主机层面限制运行 SATAN 的机器出站连接至外部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0151"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0313.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1331","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1331.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1098","title":"BSD Telnet 客户端加密会话信息泄漏漏洞","description":"BSD Telnet 客户端在实现加密与 Kerberos 4 认证功能时存在会话加密强度不足的漏洞。远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探方式捕获 Telnet 会话流量，由于加密机制存在缺陷，攻击者能够解密并窃取会话中的敏感信息（如明文密码、传输数据等）。该漏洞影响使用 BSD Telnet 客户端且启用了加密和 Kerberos 4 认证的系统，攻击者只需与目标处于同一网络路径即可实施嗅探攻击，无需任何认证权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-03-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:43.067","remediation":"立即停止使用 Telnet 协议远程登录，全面迁移至 SSH（OpenSSH 7.0 及以上版本）作为替代方案。如无法立即迁移，在服务端禁用 Kerberos 4 认证支持（配置 `/etc/inetd.conf` 移除 telnet 的 `-a kerberos4` 参数），并在防火墙层面阻断 Telnet 端口（23/TCP）的外部访问。将 BSD Telnet 客户端升级至包含该修复的最新版本或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1995-03.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/f-12.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/516.php","http://www.osvdb.org/4881"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1331.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1258","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1243","title":"SGI IRIX Desktop Permissions Tool 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.0.1 及更早版本中的 Desktop Permissions Tool（桌面权限工具）存在权限管理缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该工具修改任意文件的权限设置，从而获取对敏感系统文件的读写权限，最终实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 IRIX 5.2 和 6.0 系列版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，无需额外认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1243"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1995-03-03T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:01.407","remediation":"升级 IRIX 至 6.1 或更高版本以修复 Desktop Permissions Tool 权限提升漏洞。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 `chmod 0 /usr/sbin/desktop_perms` 移除工具执行权限，或移除其 setuid 位 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/desktop_perms`，限制本地用户任意修改文件权限的能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-16.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2113","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20263","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1243.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1243","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1243.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1243.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-99r3-j6wr-m6hm/GHSA-99r3-j6wr-m6hm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1243.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000064.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ef4c21a5-c867-4749-9a05-0f07e79ab73d.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1258.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0427","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0242","title":"Slackware Linux POP3 邮件文件未授权访问漏洞","description":"部分 Linux 系统（如 Slackware）的 POP3 邮件服务存在认证绕过漏洞，当系统启用影子密码（shadow passwords）时，POP3 守护进程未能正确验证用户凭证，远程攻击者无需有效账号即可通过 POP3 协议访问目标系统上的邮件文件，导致敏感信息泄露。攻击复杂度低，危害较大。受影响系统包括使用 shadow passwords 机制的早期 Linux 发行版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0242"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.133","remediation":"升级 Slackware Linux 的 POP3 守护进程 (如 popper) 到已修复版本，或禁用 POP3 服务改用 IMAP+SSL。确保 /etc/shadow 文件权限为 400 且仅 root 可读，避免使用未加密的 POP3 协议传输密码。如系统已不再维护，建议迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0242","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0242.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0242.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x81000/80898/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0427.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0420","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0420.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0235","title":"NCSA httpd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA httpd 1.4.1 及更早版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标 Web 服务器发送特制请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，攻击者利用此漏洞可完全控制受影响系统，危害严重。目前官方已停止维护该软件，建议用户升级至其他受支持的 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0235"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:58.270","remediation":"NCSA httpd 已停止维护多年，官方不再发布安全更新。建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server（最新稳定版为 2.4.68），该服务器由 NCSA httpd 衍生而来，兼容原有配置且持续提供安全支持。迁移后注意关闭不必要的 CGI 脚本并配置最低权限运行服务进程以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0235","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0235","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0235.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-73j6-752c-7hrj/GHSA-73j6-752c-7hrj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0235.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ed289855-2ebf-495d-9754-266d2c9ea1e7.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0420.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0417","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0232","title":"NCSA HTTPD 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 版本在处理 HTTP 请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标 Web 服务器发送超长或特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致远程代码执行或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，且无需认证即可利用。由于该软件已停止维护，建议用户迁移至 Apache httpd 等受支持的 Web 服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0232"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:57.893","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 NCSA HTTPd 1.5c，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至活跃维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上限制对 80/TCP 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0232","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0232.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0232.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83083/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0417.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0189","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0189.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0077","title":"Linux Kernel 2.2 TCP 初始序列号可预测漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2 版本 TCP 协议栈存在 TCP 初始序列号（ISN）可预测漏洞，远程攻击者可通过预测目标系统 TCP 连接的初始序列号，伪造 TCP 数据包实施会话劫持或欺骗攻击，导致未经授权的数据访问或服务中断。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.2 系列内核，攻击者只需掌握目标连接的序列号生成规律即可利用，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0077"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1995-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.603","remediation":"建议升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.26 以上版本，或迁移至 2.4.x/2.6.x 系列内核以获得 RFC 1948 TCP ISN 随机化支持。如无法升级内核，可通过 `echo 1 > /proc/sys/net/ipv4/tcp_syncookies` 启用 SYN Cookies 缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/139"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0189.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1468","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1468.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1305","title":"SCO UNIX at 程序本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UNIX 4.2 及更早版本中的 \"at\" 计划任务程序存在权限配置缺陷，本地已登录的普通用户可利用该程序的安全漏洞将自身权限提升至 root 超级用户。该漏洞影响运行 SCO UNIX 4.2 及之前版本的系统，攻击条件为攻击者需先在目标主机上获得本地普通用户访问权限，随后通过调用存在缺陷的 \"at\" 程序实现本地权限提升（LPE）。利用方式无需远程网络访问，仅依赖本地账户即可完成提权，从而获得系统的完全控制权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1305"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.447","remediation":"升级至 SCO UNIX 5.x 或更高版本，该版本已修复 at 程序的权限缺陷。临时缓解措施：移除 /usr/bin/at 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/at），并通过 /etc/at.allow 文件限制仅授权用户可使用 at 命令，防止普通用户以此提升为 root 权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-05.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1305.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1305","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1305.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1305.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fr5w-v8vm-m563/GHSA-fr5w-v8vm-m563.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1305.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--e917f4b2-4548-4b12-a6f6-d9a54a545ade.owl","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1468.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1467","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1467.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1304","title":"SCO UNIX 登录本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UNIX 4.2 及更早版本的 login 程序存在访问权限验证漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 login 程序发送特制的认证请求，绕过正常的权限检查机制，从而获取 root 超级用户权限。该漏洞允许已拥有系统低权限账户的攻击者实现权限提升，完全控制目标系统，包括读取、修改任意文件及执行任意命令。此漏洞影响 SCO UNIX 4.2 及之前版本，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1304"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.323","remediation":"官方已在 SCO UNIX 后续版本中修复该 login 权限提升漏洞。建议立即升级至 SCO UNIX 5.x 或更高版本；由于 SCO UNIX 已停止技术支持，更推荐迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Linux）。若无法升级，可采取临时缓解措施：在 /etc/default/su 中限制 login 和 su 命令仅允许 wheel 组成员执行，并移除不必要的本地用户账号以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-05.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1304.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1304","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1304.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1304.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-676g-6cqj-884c/GHSA-676g-6cqj-884c.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1304.json","https://github.com/tineshsakthir/CVE-NVD-cybersecurity/blob/1e862018eeb47a42171f56661ae478a379aeda52/server/src/logs/reqLog.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--cc9d3477-7096-4f32-aec9-d7ca37599619.owl","https://github.com/cmjayasinghe/Threat-Intelligence-Dashboard/blob/ccfec8014cc85c9e776b8f657bdb7879139ab5ed/data/cves.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1467.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1466","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1466.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1303","title":"SCO UNIX 4.2 prwarn 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UNIX 4.2 及之前版本中的 prwarn 程序存在安全漏洞，本地普通用户可通过向该程序发送特制参数触发缓冲区溢出或权限处理缺陷，从而获取 root 超级用户权限。该漏洞影响 SCO UNIX 4.2 及更早版本，攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限方可利用，危害等级高。目前厂商已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1303"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.200","remediation":"该漏洞影响已停止维护的 SCO UNIX 4.2 及更早版本，厂商未发布官方补丁。建议立即升级至受支持的现代操作系统（如 Linux 或 BSD 发行版）；若无法升级，可移除 prwarn 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/prwarn）以阻断本地提权路径，并严格限制本地用户登录权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-05.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1303.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1303","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1303.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1303.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rr93-7jxg-p4qq/GHSA-rr93-7jxg-p4qq.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1303.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--b921a81c-1bc1-4ab6-a13a-2d418a18a9ff.owl","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-1999.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1466.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1465","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1465.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1302","title":"SCO UNIX pt_chmod 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO UNIX 4.2 及更早版本中的 pt_chmod 程序存在未指明安全漏洞。pt_chmod 是一个用于修改伪终端设备权限的 setuid 程序，由于对调用者权限的检查不充分，本地用户可利用该漏洞将自身权限提升至 root，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1302"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1994-11-30T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:09.070","remediation":"立即应用 SCO 提供的 SSE005 安全补丁（pt_chmod Enhancement），可从 ftp.sco.com 的 /SSE/ 目录获取 sse005.tar.Z；升级至 SCO UNIX 3.2 v4.2 以上已修复版本。临时缓解措施：以 root 身份执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/pt_chmod 移除该程序的 setuid 权限位。SCO UNIX 系列产品已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统以保障长期安全。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/f-05.shtml","http://ftp.cerias.purdue.edu/pub/advisories/cert/cert_bulletins/VB-94:01.sco","http://www.osvdb.org/8797","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7586","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1302.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-199